Steven Murray, Country Manager, Zomato South AfricaThe day kicked off on a high note, with Zomato South Africa&#x2019;s Country Manager, Steven Murray, speaking at HOST-ED about finding gaps and working within changing industries. The third and final day will include the prize giving for the Barista Champs as well as SACA&#x2019;s Competition Zone in The Skillery. A Celebrity Cook-off at the Global Pizza Challenge area will round off the action. In the HOST-ED theatre, the final day opening will be delivered by Imameleng Mothebe, the Department of Trade and Industry&#x2019;s Director of Agro Processing Industrial Development division. A panel discussion around the proposed national liquor Amendment Act will focus on the industry implications. The NAA (National Accommodation of South Africa) will also be hosting a workshop in the morning.